(1040, 'mec_custom_msg_2_html', '<link rel = \"stylesheet\" type = \"text/css\" href = \"https://webnus.net/modern-events-calendar/addons-api/mec-extra-content/style2.css\" /><div class=\"mec-custom-msg-2-notification-set-box extra\"><div class=\"w-row mec-custom-msg-notification-wrap\"><div class=\"w-col-sm-12\"><div class=\"w-clearfix w-box mec-cmsg-2-notification-box-wrap mec-new-addons-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:0;\"><div class=\"w-box-head\">Announcement<span><i class=\"mec-sl-close\"></i></span></div><div class=\"w-box-content\"><div class=\"mec-addons-notification-box-image\"> <img src=\"https://webnus.net/modern-events-calendar/addons-api/mec-extra-content/advanced-importer-addon-banner.png\" /></div><div class=\"mec-addons-notification-box-content mec-new-addons\"><div class=\"w-box-content\"><div class=\"mec-addons-notification-title\">Advanced Importer Addon</div><p>With this addon, you can connect to Facebook, Google, Meetup, and Eventbrite and etc… unlimitedly. This makes the import process so easy. You should authenticate your account with just a few clicks and plan the import process. Also, with this plugin you can have more third-party plugins for importing. You should initiate the process from a WordPress on which MEC is installed.</p><strong>Key Features:</strong><div class=\"mec-addons-key-features\"><ul><li>Multiple Accounts</li><li>Planned Import</li><li>Setting A Status For Import</li><li>Category Setting For Import</li><li>Setting Start/End Date For Import</li><li>Setting Special Events For Import</li><li>Importing From URL/File</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div><a href=\"https://webnus.net/modern-events-calendar/addons/advanced-importer/?ref=17\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'yes'),
